Which type of reasoning can be used for each of the following statements?
=====


1. Based on a recent survey, the fraction of the population that prefer sweet to wour is between 73 and 76 percent.
[[
Bayesian reasoning
(Frequentist reasoning)
]]

2. There is a 20% chance of rain tomorrow.
[[
(Bayesian reasoning)
Frequentist reasoning
]]

3. I will bet you 20$ to 1$ that my football team would win tomorrow's match.
[[
(Bayesian reasoning)
Frequentist reasoning
]]

4. The chance that two random people have the same birthday is at least 1/365.
[[
Bayesian reasoning
(Frequentist reasoning)
]]
